know yet what caused the accident on coastal us route 1 saturday 
afternoon priors car crossed the center line and hit a travel 
tours of oklahoma bus taking 47 people to newfoundland all of the 
dead were people in the car twenty others were injured 
one of the few witnesses to the accident indicated that the 
car veered into the northbound lane for 30 to 40 yards and did not 
attempt to take evasive action spokesman stephen mccausland of 
the maine public safety department said sunday the witness was a 
passenger on the bus he said 
